## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **sparsentan Filspari 2023** = first FDA dual ETA + AT1 antagonist IgAN, PROTECT trial 양성. ETA + AT1 dual single-molecule paradigm — IgAN 단백뇨 + GFR preservation. quantum-VQE 의 dual-target single-molecule pocket leverage.
2. **nefecon Tarpeyo 2023** = first FDA targeted-release budesonide IgAN, NefIgArd trial 양성. Peyer's patch ileum 직접 mucosal IgA1 생성 억제. systemic corticosteroid TESTING trial 2017 long-term safety 의문 → local mucosal-targeted paradigm shift.
3. **iptacopan Fabhalta 2024 IgAN expansion** = first FDA factor B oral, 2023 PNH 후 2024 IgAN expansion. C-pathway alternative pathway 차단 → mesangial C3 deposition 억제. quantum-VQE factor B pocket cross-iag.
4. **APRIL/BAFF Phase 3 폭발 (sibeprenlimab + povetacicept + atacicept + telitacicept) 2024-2026** = gd-IgA1 생성 → APRIL/BAFF 의존 plasma cell survival 차단. IgAN pathogenesis 의 mechanism-based 첫 paradigm. mAb 다발성 → small-molecule next-gen 가능성.
5. **SGLT2i (empagliflozin + dapagliflozin + canagliflozin) EMPA-KIDNEY + DAPA-CKD + CREDENCE 2019-2023** = IgAN subgroup 양성. RAAS 너머 만성 신장 보호 새로운 mechanism. tubuloglomerular feedback + intraglomerular pressure 경감.
6. **finerenone Kerendia 2021** = non-steroidal MR antagonist DKD + 만성 신장 보호. spironolactone/eplerenone 의 hyperkalemia 부담 경감 + 단백뇨 추가 감소. quantum-VQE MR selectivity pocket.
7. **atrasentan Phase 3 ALIGN** = ETA selective Phase 3 IgAN. sparsentan dual 의 ETA component 만으로 충분한지, 또는 dual 이 우월한지 head-to-head 비교 미정.
8. **avacopan Tavneos 2021** = C5aR ANCA vasculitis. crescentic IgAN + IgA vasculitis 만성 → C-pathway terminal 차단 IgAN research 확장.
9. **TESTING trial 2017** = systemic full-dose methylprednisolone IgAN long-term safety 의문 (감염 + osteonecrosis). 의문이 nefecon ileum-local paradigm 으로 이동.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, IgAN 임상 의미 한정. K-IgAN 한국 multicenter registry + KDIGO 2021 + 2024 update 와의 alignment 만 indirect.

